article_title: Israeli operations in Gaza will resume with full force after truce, says Netanyahu.
sentence: Gaza's  Hamas-run  health  ministry  says  more  than  14,500  people,  including  at  least  5,500  children,  have  been  killed  in  Gaza  since  Israel  began  attacking  the  territory  in  reprisal  for  the  7  October  attacks.
